          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646237162983-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the freekeh is cooking, combine the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar </strong>with half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>, 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining wholegrain mustard for another recipe!</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>balsamic-mustard dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1589819724163-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1589819724163-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1589819724163-x700.jpg",
