          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1589819732796-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1589819732796-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1589819732796-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>broccoli & freekeh </strong>over the<strong> rocket</strong>, then top with the<strong> chopped bacon </strong>and <strong>roasted grapes</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>balsamic-mustard dressing</strong> all over and season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
